    needs to be changed in one place (debian/rules) rather than
    search-and-replacing debian/control
  * Remove debian/make-substvars and incorporate its logic into debian/rules

 -- Matt Zimmerman <mdz@ubuntu.com>  Wed,  3 Aug 2005 14:11:58 -0700

