    . include/net/xfrm.h
    . net/xfrm/xfrm_policy.c
    . net/xfrm/xfrm_state.c
  * Fixed inclusion loop with include/net/sctp/sm.h:
    . include/net/sctp/sctp.h
    . net/sctp/associola.c
    . net/sctp/outqueue.c
    . net/sctp/socket.c
    . net/sctp/transport.c
