    closes: #218670).
  * Initialise state for /proc/net/tcp in net/ipv4/tcp_ipv4.c (bk).
  * Cleaned up debian/rules a little.
  * Schedule tasklets for async removal in drivers/usb/host/uhci-hcd.*.

